# Cloudflare Pages security headers for the Jobdun admin console.
# These are all safe for a Flutter/CanvasKit + Supabase app. A strict CSP and
# COOP/COEP are a deliberate next step — added via CSP-Report-Only + a test pass
# first (they can white-screen CanvasKit if set blind), then promoted to enforce.
/*
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=(), payment=(), usb=()
